snippet.title: PlayStation All-Stars Battle Royale - Isaac Clarke Trailer
snippet.description:
PlayStation® All-Stars Battle Royale™ is free-for-all brawler featuring the greatest stars in the PlayStation universe! Unleash the power of the RIG suit and an arsenal of weapons as Isaac Clarke joins the fight!
